Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:09.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比方说在冬日的某一天 计划着一次快乐的旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.05,0:00:12.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与往常不一样的兴奋感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.69,0:00:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍稍脱离平常日子的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.86,0:00:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以洋溢着欢笑的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.79,0:00:27.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定在想像着美好的将来 话怎么也停不下来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.74,0:00:31.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然预定一直都定不下来 但却是如此的快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.43,0:00:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这短暂的幸福 现在也宛如遥远的过去一般…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:44.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样滑雪的准备工作就完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.34,0:02:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 离准备好打包还差很远哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.25,0:02:55.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,创伤药旅馆也会有的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:59.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呀 毕竟没人知道什么时候会受伤的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五点就会有人来接了 在那之前做好准备哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.85,0:03:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:25.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天禁止熬夜哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.04,0:03:26.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.70,0:03:30.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得的机会 这次的旅行一定要尽兴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我想这之后一定会有不少事在等着我们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.66,0:03:59.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 既然事态演变到了这地步
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要跟两位说的事也就只有一件了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.21,0:04:04.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的午饭是大碗咖喱饭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.72,0:04:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杉並 你 你这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.17,0:04:13.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,涉 快意识到你的失败全是因为想法太天真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.43,0:04:17.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别胡说 我可是拼了命才活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.27,0:04:19.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人生的一切都是靠我这双手…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.00,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.20,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这家伙 义之你太卑鄙了 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要考虑清楚啊 涉 这可是要决定你的一生啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别多管闲事啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,中啦 午餐就由你请客啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,输啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:39.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 你没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.85,0:04:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才没那回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.59,0:04:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为不是靠窗的位置 所以生气了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我又不是小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.67,0:04:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之 下一局要开始了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这局就来赌甜点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.83,0:05:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然雪在初音岛算不上罕见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.47,0:05:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但却没有积到这般程度的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可挑剔的雪量
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.31,0:05:13.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 这么看来可以尽情地滑了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:14.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.36,0:05:18.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这种场面可是我梦寐以求的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.25,0:05:19.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场面？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪场不是经常会有恋情降临吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.35,0:05:25.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你果然是在想那些啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.02,0:05:28.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舍华求实改成舍雪求女了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,旅店是在那边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:32.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 对 就是那边
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:35.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么等放下行李就去滑雪场吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.35,0:05:36.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.67,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说 咦？ 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.13,0:05:57.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么 应该都好了吧 大家集合
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.79,0:05:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？ 由梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.77,0:06:02.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像因为长途旅行比较累了 在房间里休息呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 好像她在车上也没什么精神呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.24,0:06:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟乘完船乘电车又换公车才到的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:13.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难得都来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:15.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.21,0:06:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事的没事的 稍微休息一下就会好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.01,0:06:20.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们去滑雪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦幻之花园路线不是挺漂亮的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.85,0:06:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那里是中级路线了 首先应该滑初级路线哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.40,0:06:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我… 到底想要怎么做呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.96,0:06:59.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一二 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然厉害呢 那两人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:06.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要逃避现实哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.10,0:07:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 继续吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.50,0:07:10.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续 一二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.24,0:07:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.15,0:07:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.52,0:07:16.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 小恋 等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.63,0:07:20.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.23,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大腿内侧好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.12,0:07:25.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像没受伤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:27.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜抱歉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.14,0:07:30.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,动 动不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.80,0:07:32.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.36,0:07:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站 站不起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别慌别慌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.29,0:07:38.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先把周围的雪压平
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:44.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 快 太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.58,0:07:46.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷静点 板桥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.09,0:07:49.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你并没有那么快 多利用一下滑雪板边
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果我能办到就用不着这么辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.97,0:07:53.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀 那边看来也很辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.02,0:07:55.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 摔倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了板桥 就这样子你可抓不住滑雪场的恋情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.90,0:08:03.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.11,0:08:07.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你们没事吧？ 要帮忙吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.36,0:08:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小恋 你处于劣势哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.21,0:08:10.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？ 你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:20.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到头来由梦她也没来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 感觉怎么样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.94,0:08:25.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:28.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就稍微去滑一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来下午也没有看到小恋呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.45,0:08:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是去堆雪人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.31,0:08:38.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因为人家…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:40.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一共做了几个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.38,0:08:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家4代共28个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.71,0:08:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做了那么多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.35,0:08:46.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就在想为什么你完全没过来滑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.83,0:08:49.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟一开始只想堆一对情侣出来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.15,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前也干过这种事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干过…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.84,0:08:55.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时候做了多少个呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.84,0:08:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一家6代共35个
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.58,0:09:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,板桥君 你那摔的也太多了点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错 声音也很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,话说杏你也是新手吧 为什么那么厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.64,0:09:16.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是记忆力的差别
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哦 活动身体这种事原来光靠记忆力就能办到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.68,0:09:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说到底都是受在大脑的突触控制的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.39,0:09:25.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.02,0:09:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确实只有在料理这方面能够自豪一番呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.27,0:09:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肚子好饱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.83,0:09:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么等泡了澡后就在男生房间集合吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.17,0:09:38.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 你身体已经没事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何 去滑夜场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:45.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:50.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.91,0:09:57.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.54,0:09:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.17,0:10:09.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.38,0:10:13.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟今天活动了一天 得好好放松下才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.88,0:10:15.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说谁运动过了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.62,0:10:19.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我真的是活动过身体的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:23.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然你那么累 那我就来帮你放松下好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.77,0:10:28.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由茜姐姐我的…手指神技来帮你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.15,0:10:30.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,茜你说这种话总觉得很下流啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.50,0:10:32.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我本来就是怎么色就怎么说的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那手势也太下流了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.77,0:10:40.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么白河同学如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:44.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我 我… 就算了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.18,0:10:46.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,两位请不要客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.38,0:10:47.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.53,0:10:51.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行啦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,工口吗 工口吗 两位的这里…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:58.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 这堵墙的另一面明明就是天国…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.19,0:11:01.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我好想游过去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:06.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,俗物 比起实物还是声音更能让人有想像的空间啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.43,0:11:10.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来如此 在那种地方竟有着那样的痣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.01,0:11:13.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么！？ 那样的痣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.38,0:11:14.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想游过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.46,0:11:17.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 原来也能够像那样笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:19.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去滑夜场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.78,0:11:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.67,0:11:28.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了呢 由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:31.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 不 没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.99,0:11:40.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说起来 小时候的由梦在跟我一起的时候经常笑着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.44,0:11:47.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是从什么时候开始的呢 由梦再也不那样对我笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.33,0:12:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 差不多该走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:20.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪里… 当然是弟弟君他们的房间啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.82,0:12:32.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,觉得好紧张啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:34.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个纯情小男人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.39,0:12:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.68,0:12:37.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎光临
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.12,0:12:39.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.22,0:12:40.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭候多时了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.64,0:12:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打搅了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.14,0:12:44.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我特意买来了比塔饼让大家保持战斗情绪哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.95,0:12:46.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真贴心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.72,0:12:53.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 由梦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.88,0:12:55.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次是说泡澡泡得有些晕堂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.13,0:13:15.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晕堂的话需要多补充水分
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:20.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.20,0:14:13.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从什么地方来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.44,0:14:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一起滑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.33,0:14:17.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.56,0:14:21.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 请你…住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.24,0:14:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快躲开
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.28,0:14:29.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你 还真敢干
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:30.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放 放手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:32.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这什么态度
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.84,0:14:35.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,搭理你个丑八怪是你的福气
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.79,0:14:37.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别小看人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.19,0:14:39.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.99,0:14:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.41,0:14:50.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们是都是初学…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这下搞定了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:00.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.35,0:15:03.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.47,0:15:11.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,晕堂了所以出来凉快一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.89,0:15:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.51,0:15:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,继续滑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.39,0:15:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.79,0:15:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.94,0:15:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一个人就…不 要不一起 不行…那样又会…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.81,0:15:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.10,0:15:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.74,0:15:47.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.74,0:15:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:51.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要来 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.56,0:15:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来的话 哥哥也会遇难的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:01.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天这家伙 为什么躲着我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.77,0:16:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.21,0:16:26.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.65,0:16:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:40.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.47,0:17:11.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.97,0:17:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.44,0:17:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快回答
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.07,0:17:21.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.98,0:17:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.41,0:17:25.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行 这样下去的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.03,0:17:27.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.38,0:17:31.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不避开哥哥 哥哥也会遇难的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.78,0:17:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,疼 疼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.49,0:17:38.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不赶快避开的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.90,0:17:46.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.05,0:17:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥…哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:58.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.80,0:18:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.43,0:18:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.32,0:18:03.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:06.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚摔伤了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.37,0:18:08.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别说话了 现在就把你挖出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哥哥 为什么要来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.81,0:18:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.49,0:18:20.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样下去的话 会遇难的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.14,0:18:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,梦会变成现实
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.96,0:18:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做梦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.38,0:18:32.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.14,0:18:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和我一起遇难的梦吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.98,0:18:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.07,0:18:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事 不会遇难的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:45.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:46.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.04,0:18:50.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.17,0:18:57.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由梦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.63,0:18:59.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到滑雪场了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.70,0:19:01.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.10,0:19:03.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没遇难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.89,0:19:14.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.83,0:19:16.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还差一点路
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.94,0:19:19.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们慢慢走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.83,0:19:20.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.59,0:19:23.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那不是噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.01,0:19:25.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.40,0:19:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,未来还是无法改变的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.09,0:19:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算那样 我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.48,0:19:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一号签 去给大家买果汁
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.55,0:19:49.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么又是我 当我是跑腿的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.29,0:19:55.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,平时的话都是义之中招的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.66,0:19:59.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 那家伙莫非知道会这样才逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.58,0:20:01.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,辛苦啦 呆鸭二号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.32,0:20:02.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘎嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.90,0:20:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,义之 你跑哪去了
